  <content_rating type="oars-1.1" />

  <description>
    <p>Have always at a glance the usage of system resources</p>

    <p>Monitorets is a small utility application offering a simple and quick view at the usage of several of your computer resources. Almost like an applet or a widget for your desktop.</p>

    <p>Available monitors:</p>
     <ul>
      <li>Cpu</li>
      <li>Gpu (experimental support)</li>
      <li>Memory</li>
      <li>Swap</li>
      <li>Network downlink traffic</li>
      <li>Network uplink traffic</li>
      <li>Home folder space</li>
      <li>Root space</li>
      <li>Temperature sensors</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

